column5: Sorry to waist your time guy's but this dude looks quite like a good buddy of mine off this board...but i need all your help in confirming that he is in fact an elf ....i couldnt believe my eye's when i first saw it~! pmsl  http://www.elfyourself.com/?userid=452df65...3a1a43G06121418
That's weird. He wore the same costume and did the exact same dance the entire 3 days that I spent with him last September.
Oh Iv'e seen him dance like that before, not a pretty site. I am very afraid to share a boat with him.
Hmmmmm......that elf does indeed look familiar...
Dang I near wet my drawers when I saw him dancing~! Guess thats just my bent sense of humour~!
Oh when Cupcake reads this thread, we are not gonna be popular guys!  How long before he clicks on this thread, any bets?
